            "title": "德法股市創約半個月低　英股微升續創新高",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">歐洲股市大多偏軟，市場關注美國聯儲局及歐洲央行12月會議或有較大分歧，利率不確定影響市場情緒。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：德國證交所官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250306_FI_source-web_eu-stock-2.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：德國證交所官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250306_FI_source-web_eu-stock-2.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：德國證交所官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">泛歐指數Stoxx 600收市回吐0.1%，報574點，最多曾挫0.61%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">德法股市連跌3日，德國DAX指數收報24118點，跌5點，跌幅0.02%，創近兩星期新低。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">法國CAC指數收報8157點，跌43點，跌幅0.53%，是半個月收市新低。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">英國富時100指數微升3點或0.04%，收報9760點，連升9日，再創新高。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">意大利富時MIB指數收報43202點，跌0.09%或40點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">西班牙IBEX 35指數收報16040點，下挫0.68%或109點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">渣打集團(02888)第三季除稅前列賬基準溢利按年升2.56%，倫敦股價升3.6%，收報1571便士。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">空中巴士(Airbus)第三季表現超出分析員預期，經營收入增長14%至178億歐羅，營業利潤上升42%至17.5億歐羅，股價收市攀升2.1%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">殼牌(Shell)第三季利潤大幅下滑，經調整後純利報54億美元，仍超出分析員預期，集團宣布將在未來三個月回購35億美元的股票，股價一度跌0.9%，收市反覆回升0.2%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15384928-%e5%be%b7%e6%b3%95%e8%82%a1%e5%b8%82%e5%89%b5%e7%b4%84%e5%8d%8a%e5%80%8b%e6%9c%88%e4%bd%8e%e3%80%80%e8%8b%b1%e8%82%a1%e5%be%ae%e5%8d%87%e7%ba%8c%e5%89%b5%e6%96%b0%e9%ab%98",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250318_FI_source-ap_Britain_Financial_Markets-2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-31 07:55:34",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美股道指曾跌250點　納指跌1.59%　Meta挫逾11%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美股3大指數都跌，道指及標普500指數連跌兩個交易日。Meta及微軟股價急挫，人工智能(AI)開支急升引發憂慮。聯儲局主席鮑威爾偏鷹派言論，市場對減息預期降溫。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"美股 (AP圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/20250804_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"美股 (AP圖片)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/20250804_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">美股 (AP圖片)</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">道瓊斯工業平均指數低開185點後，跌幅一度擴大至250點，隨後在多隻金融股造好帶動下，倒升最多382點，高見48014點，最終回吐超過100點，收市報47522點，跌109點，跌幅0.23%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">標普500指數收報6822點，跌68點，跌幅1.01%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">納斯達克指數扭轉5日升勢，回吐幅度較大，收報23581點，跌377點或1.59%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">Meta大跌11.3%，創3年來最大單日跌幅，上季業績受到一次性稅務費用拖累而大跌。據報集團發債接獲1250億美元認購額，創公開市場企業發債紀錄新高，預料發債規模至少250億美元。市場也擔心人工智能(AI)相關資本開支過多。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">微軟跌2.9%，上季資本開支近350億美元創新高。Nvidia及Tesla分別跌2%及近5%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">Alphabet雲端業務表現突出，股價一度抽升6.2%，收市仍漲2.5%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">Netflix收市後宣布1拆10股份，以降低股價，市後時段股價升逾3%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">收市後公布業績的蘋果及亞馬遜，盤後時段分別升近4%及逾13%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">另外，波音再跌逾6%，連續兩日急挫，股價創逾4個月新低。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15384900-%e7%be%8e%e8%82%a1%e9%81%93%e6%8c%87%e6%9b%be%e8%b7%8c250%e9%bb%9e%e3%80%80%e7%b4%8d%e6%8c%87%e8%b7%8c1-59%e3%80%80meta%e6%8c%ab%e9%80%be11",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250730_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-31 07:50:36",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
